{"title":"fix(remediation): correct vigil-app image tag to resolve ImagePullBackOff","body":"Root cause: Deployment vigil-app specifies non-existent image tag nginx:declared-missing in declared manifest, causing ImagePullBackOff on new pods.

Evidence: Warning   Failed                Error: ErrImagePull ... Failed to pull image "nginx:live-missing": rpc error: code = NotFound desc = failed to pull and unpack image "docker.io/library/nginx:live-missing": failed to resolve reference "docker.io/library/nginx:live-missing": docker.io/library/nginx:live-missing: not found

Fix: Updated image tag from nginx:declared-missing to nginx:1.25 in infra/overlays/hetzner/kubernetes/clusters/hetzner/apps/vigil-app.yaml"}
